<%
  tournament_name = @tournament&.name || 'the tournament'
  team_count = (@sponsor.slot_count.to_i / 2.0).ceil
  player_count = @sponsor.slot_count.to_i
  contact_name = @tournament&.contact_name.presence || @org_name
  contact_phone = @tournament&.contact_phone
  contact_email = @tournament&.respond_to?(:contact_email) ? @tournament.contact_email : nil
%>
Sponsor Portal Access — <%= tournament_name %>

Hello <%= @sponsor.name %>,

Thank you for sponsoring <%= tournament_name %>!
<% if player_count > 0 %>You have <%= team_count %> team<%= team_count == 1 ? '' : 's' %> (<%= player_count %> player<%= player_count == 1 ? '' : 's' %>) to register.<% end %>

Access your sponsor portal here:
<%= @access_url %>

This link expires in 7 days.

<% if @tournament&.sponsor_edit_deadline.present? %>
DEADLINE: Player information must be submitted by <%= @tournament.sponsor_edit_deadline.strftime('%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p') %>.
<% elsif @tournament&.check_in_time.present? && @tournament&.event_date.present? %>
DEADLINE: Player information must be submitted by <%= @tournament.check_in_time %> on <%= @tournament.event_date.is_a?(Date) ? @tournament.event_date.strftime('%B %-d, %Y') : @tournament.event_date %>.
<% end %>

Questions? Contact <%= contact_name %><%= " at #{contact_phone}" if contact_phone.present? %><%= " or #{contact_email}" if contact_email.present? %>.

<%= @org_name %>
